Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Presidential campaign begins
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99d5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Feb 1976
Hopefuls line up for start of this year's presidential campaign. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.